[The country of Malawi, officially the Republic of Malawi, is a landlocked country in south east Africa that was formerly known as Nyasaland. It is bordered by Zambia to the north west, Tanzania to the north east, and Mozambique on the east, south and west. It can be seen on a map at http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/malawi.pdf. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be seen at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5658608,176. - Mod.LL]

